This file describes format of url.list

Channel to EPG data mapping is provided by url.list file present in the cPlugins::Configdirectory("xmlepg2vdr) directory. (for eg. in my machine it is /etc/vdr/plugins/xmlepg2vdr/url.list) See below for the FORMAT of url.list file.


------------------FORMAT OF url.list FILE----------
CHANNEL1 NAME; URL1
CHANNEL2 NAME; URL2
BBC 1; http://www.bleb.org/tv/data/listings/0/bbc1.xml
---------------------------END FILE----------------

No blank lines allowed. 
Spaces in Channel name allowed but Channel names should be terminated by a ';' character (no spaces before ';')



